---
title: DeepSeek 最新技術資訊大廳 - 跨境AI站群推文列表
layout: layout.njk
description: "專業的 DeepSeek 核心資訊大廳。為您實時聚合展示關於2026年AI多開策略、跨境防關聯技術、官方最新升級公告等全量優質繁體技術文章列表，內置強大SEO分頁組件。"
pagination:
  data: collections.posts
  size: 10
  alias: posts
permalink: "blog/{% if pagination.pageNumber > 0 %}page-{{ pagination.pageNumber }}/{% endif %}index.html"
---

<style>
    .list-h1 { font-size: 24px; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 25px; border-bottom: 2px solid #0052cc; padding-bottom: 10px; }
    .article-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
    .article-card { border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 25px; border-radius: 8px; background: #fff; }
    .article-card h2 { font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 10px 0; }
    .article-card h2 a { color: #0f172a; }
    .article-card h2 a:hover { color: #0052cc; }
    .article-meta { font-size: 13px; color: #94a3b8; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .article-excerpt { font-size: 14px; color: #475569; line-height: 1.6; text-align: justify; }
    
    /* 分頁導航樣式 */
    .pagination-nav { margin-top: 40px; display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 10px; align-items: center; }
    .page-link { padding: 8px 14px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e1; border-radius: 4px; background: white; font-size: 14px; color: #475569; }
    .page-link:hover { background: #f1f5f9; color: #0052cc; border-color: #0052cc; }
    .page-active { padding: 8px 14px; background: #0052cc; color: white; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; border: 1px solid #0052cc; }
    .page-disabled { padding: 8px 14px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 4px; color: #cbd5e1; background: #f8fafc; font-size: 14px; cursor: not-allowed; }
</style>

{# 🌟 核心SEO修復：列表頁唯一的 h1，留給欄目分類名稱，保障權重清晰 #}
<h1 class="list-h1">{{ title }}</h1>

{% if pagination.pageNumber > 0 %}
    <div style="color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 14px;">
        當前位置：<a href="/">首頁入口</a> &gt; <a href="/blog/">技術資訊大廳</a> &gt; 第 {{ pagination.pageNumber + 1 }} 頁
    </div>
{% endif %}

<div class="article-list">
    {% for post in posts %}
        <article class="article-card">
            <h2>
                {# 降級為 h2，保護頁面 h1 結構唯一性 #}
                <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
            </h2>
            <div class="article-meta">
                <span>📅 發布時間：{{ post.date | dateFilter }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="article-excerpt">
                {{ post.templateContent | striptags | truncate(150) }}
            </div>
        </article>
    {% endfor %}
</div>

{# 🌟 帶分頁組件的進階 SEO 導航鏈接結構 #}
<nav class="pagination-nav">
    {% if pagination.href.previous %}
        <a href="{{ pagination.href.previous }}" class="page-link">« 上一頁</a>
    {% else %}
        <span class="page-disabled">« 上一頁</span>
    {% endif %}

    {% for pageEntry in pagination.pages %}
        {% if pagination.pageNumber == loop.index0 %}
            <span class="page-active">{{ loop.index }}</span>
        {% else %}
            <a href="{{ pagination.hrefs[loop.index0] }}" class="page-link">{{ loop.index }}</a>
        {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}

    {% if pagination.href.next %}
        <a href="{{ pagination.href.next }}" class="page-link">下一頁 »</a>
    {% else %}
        <span class="page-disabled">下一頁 »</span>
    {% endif %}
</nav>